                When to use
              </h3>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14.5px;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">Record status in tables (e.g., Active, Inactive, Pending).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">Connection or availability status (e.g., Online, Offline).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">Workflow state indicators (e.g., Draft, Published, Archived).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">System health in dashboards (e.g., Healthy, Degraded, Down).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent;">Process status in lists (e.g., Running, Paused, Complete).</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 24px; background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.25s ease;">
