                When NOT to use
              </h3>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14.5px;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">For numeric counts -- use Counter instead.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; margin-bottom: 8px;">For category labels -- use Badge or Tag instead.</li>
