        <!-- Complete Do's and Don'ts -->
        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="detailed-guidelines" class="doc-section-title">Complete Do's and Don'ts</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Visual and interaction guidelines to ensure Status Indicators are effective and accessible.</p>
          <div class="do-dont-grid">
            <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Consistent mapping:</strong> Use the same status-to-color mapping throughout the entire application.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Include labels:</strong> Always include a text label when the meaning isn't obvious from context.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Dense layouts:</strong> Use Small size for data tables and lists where space is limited.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Semantic consistency:</strong> Neutral=idle, Success=online, Warning=degraded, Critical=error, Info=informational.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span>
              <ul class="doc-list" style="border: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Too many types:</strong> Don't use more than 5 status types in a single view.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Color-only:</strong> Don't rely solely on dot color -- always include a label for accessibility.</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Wrong component:</strong> Don't use for numeric counts (use Counter) or categories (use Badge/Tag).</li>
                <li style="border: none; background: transparent; padding-left: 20px;"><strong>Inconsistent sizing:</strong> Don't mix sizes within the same table column or list.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

